In large saucepan over low heat, melt margarine. Add marshmallows; stir until melted and well blended. Remove from heat. Stir in vanilla. Add cereal, peanuts and raisins, then chocolate chips, stirring until thoroughly coated. Using lightly-buttered spatula, press into buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9-inch) pan. Cool. Cut into bars.